title: Late Allison TD delivers Illinois win over Nebraska, 14-13
text:
Published By: Charlotte Observer: Sports - Today 
Wes Lunt hit Geronimo Allison with a 1-yard touchdown pass with 10 seconds left in the game to lead Illinois past Nebraska on Saturday, 14-1...
